wytr.dialog.???.1.1.4794f3f2: You dare enter these sewers, human? These pipes once hid the civilians of Ragni during raids... Now they just hold corpses.
wytr.dialog.???.2.1.ad179f03: Oh, it seems I have a guest. You're just in time for dinner... hehe..
wytr.dialog.???.2.2.c3f9c526: My poor babies are starving. But what shall they feast on? How about... you?
wytr.dialog.Arakadicus.1.1.0d0d69bb: You've come so far, haven't you? And my babies are just so hungry... You'll make a fine meal for them... hehehe...
wytr.dialog.Arakadicus.2.1.6da65cc0: Ah, the main course has arrived. You look so good, I think I'll have a taste of you myself!
